The United States strongly condemns the terrorist attack in Beirut that killed Lebanese Internal Security Forces Information Bureau Director Wissam al-Hassan and others. The US expresses condolences to the victims' families and supports the Lebanese people in their pursuit of security and stability. There is no justification for using assassination as a political tool, and the US will stand by Lebanon as they bring those responsible to justice. The goal is to build a future where all Lebanese can live in security and dignity.